data.description: Welcome to this stunning, remodeled 3-bedroom, 2-bathroom home that boasts an open and inviting living, dining, and kitchen space. Featuring a cozy fireplace and luxurious new flooring throughout. The kitchen is a chef's dream with custom cabinetry, stainless steel appliances, and an eat-in bar for additional seating. On the main floor, you'll find a convenient laundry room, making daily chores a breeze. The primary bedroom is a true sanctuary with a private bathroom.  With attached garage parking and a recently installed HVAC system from 2020. Upstairs offers a 3rd bedroom that can be used as an office or a bonus room. This home is a must-see.
